<!--
  Replicator · Icons.xaml · v1.0.1
  14 system icons as WPF DrawingImage resources. Add this dictionary AFTER
  Theme.xaml in App.xaml's merged dictionaries, then use:

    <Image Source="{StaticResource Icon.Backup}" Width="24" Height="24"/>

  All Brush/Pen references resolve dynamically against Theme.xaml so live
  re-theming works at runtime.

  v1.0.1 — fixed: every stroked GeometryDrawing now ships an explicit Pen.
-->
